</emphasis>
Altona Bay, St. Croix, 
<collectingCountry box="[619,669,260,284]" name="United States of America" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">U.S.</collectingCountry>
Virgin Is.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="308.[151,1437,151,1472]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,513,295,320]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">Other material examined.</emphasis>
Three additional specimens were examined: 
<number box="[1036,1050,296,320]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="1.0">1</number>
spec., 
<number box="[1133,1168,296,320]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="4.7">4.7</number>
x 2.0 mm, Cabo Rojo, Bahia Salinas, 
<collectingCountry box="[318,452,332,357]" name="Puerto Rico" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">Puerto Rico</collectingCountry>
(P. Williams coll.); 
<number box="[677,691,332,356]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="2.0">2</number>
spec., 
<number box="[769,804,332,356]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="4.7">4.7</number>
x 2.0 &amp; 
<number box="[904,939,332,356]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="4.5">4.5</number>
x 
<quantity box="[967,1055,332,356]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" unit="mm" value="1.9">1.9 mm</quantity>
, &quot;The Shacks&quot;, Jobos Bay, 
<collectingCountry name="Puerto Rico" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">Puerto Rico</collectingCountry>
(P. Williams coll.).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="308.[151,1437,151,1472]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,439,404,429]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">Range and habitat.</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[451,501,404,428]" name="United States of America" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">U.S.</collectingCountry>
Virgin Is. (St. Croix); 
<collectingCountry box="[784,926,404,429]" name="Puerto Rico" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">Puerto Rico</collectingCountry>
. Also St. Thomas (Water I.) and St. Barts according to Nowell-Usticke (
<number box="[496,555,439,464]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="1969.0">1969</number>
; 
<number box="[568,625,439,464]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" value="1971.0">1971</number>
) but not confirmed here. The depth was not stated for 
<typeStatus box="[1255,1303,440,463]" pageId="308" pageNumber="309">type</typeStatus>
specimens. Other specimens were collected in shallow water.
</paragraph>
